[Question inaudible]

55:53.340 --> 55:58.350
It is situated on top of the brain where it
is above the brain, and it is covered with,

55:58.350 --> 56:05.350
the doctors say that it is 988 nerves - because
I don’t want to quarrel with them. But there

56:09.290 --> 56:16.100
are 1000 nerves which cover it. And when it
is enlightened you’ll be surprised, you’ll

56:16.100 --> 56:23.100
see a beautiful lotus opening in all colors,
very very silent flames, and they are so peace-giving,

56:31.010 --> 56:38.010
looks so beautiful. Because when any nerve
gets enlightened, the light of that flame

56:43.060 --> 56:50.060
looks like a petal. It’s very beautiful,
it is. But it has to open out. Just now it

56:50.410 --> 56:57.109
is covered by our conditioning and our ego.
Like we have become like an egg we can say.

56:57.109 --> 57:02.170
That’s why in Sanskrit language, a person
who has known the brahma, the all-pervading

57:02.170 --> 57:09.170
power, is called as dvijaha and a bird is
also called as dvijaha - means born twice.

57:12.990 --> 57:19.990
First as an egg, then it becomes a bird – human
being and a realized soul. These are the two

58:25.410 --> 58:26.690
stages.

58:26.690 --> 58:29.260
[Question inaudible]

58:29.260 --> 58:36.260
You see the thing is that now there are social
conditions which are very bad, people are

58:36.430 --> 58:43.170
homeless, they are on the streets. Now thinking
about it you are not going to help them, are

58:43.170 --> 58:50.030
you? No. Which is the best way is to empower
yourself, all right? Now see for example,

58:50.030 --> 58:57.030
in the villages of India where I work, people
have given them alcohol, they have given up

59:00.030 --> 59:07.030
all bad habits, they have become very dynamic,
they have become very well off, they are living

59:07.050 --> 59:14.050
very well. In London, if you want to work,
I am sure you can get a home, no problem.

59:17.240 --> 59:21.850
You see the Asians who have come here, I am
an Asian though I didn’t come as an immigrant,

59:21.850 --> 59:28.850
they are becoming very rich, because they
work very hard, very hard, so those who want

59:29.290 --> 59:34.730
to… in London. But in India it may not be.
But despite that, after Sahaja Yoga they have

59:34.730 --> 59:41.050
improved so much – they have become so dynamic,
they have become so hopeful of life. But if

59:41.050 --> 59:48.050
you just think that life is good for nothing,
let us now drink and be merry then it won’t

59:49.250 --> 59:50.359
work out.

59:50.359 --> 59:55.200
These homeless and all these conditions are
all such – because it is an artificial condition

59:55.200 --> 01:00:02.200
you know, many people have houses but they
don’t want to give it for people to live.

01:00:02.350 --> 01:00:09.350
Now if those people get transformation, they
won’t behave like that. You see the whole

01:00:10.010 --> 01:00:14.980
behavior will change when the emancipation
of the society comes up. But I have seen in

01:00:14.980 --> 01:00:21.980
the villages of India there’s a complete
transformation. The social conditions are

01:00:22.340 --> 01:00:29.340
much worse but Indians are more satisfied
people, they are not so much. Here even, supposing

01:00:30.220 --> 01:00:34.960
you offer a house, they will say, “No, I
don’t like this house.” You offer a job,

01:00:34.960 --> 01:00:38.980
they’ll say, “I don’t want this job.”
All these things are there – also too much

01:00:38.980 --> 01:00:45.980
of choices. But if you decide, London is not
difficult place I tell you to work hard and

01:00:46.350 --> 01:00:53.350
get a house, not difficult, they can do it.
But people don’t work here, don’t work.

01:00:54.690 --> 01:01:00.410
There are so many old people who haven’t
got anybody to help them. But these people

01:01:00.410 --> 01:01:07.090
will never go and help them. They can earn.
This is a place where anybody can earn I think,

01:01:07.090 --> 01:01:12.180
because I know people, Asians, who have come
here without any money are very rich today

