– why? In India, I cannot think of such

01:02:28.540 --> 01:02:35.540
a thing. The reason, though they are very
poor, the reason is they know what is love.

01:02:38.270 --> 01:02:43.609
And that is what I feel that the society has
to little bit take to Sahaja Yoga.

01:02:43.609 --> 01:02:50.430
Now we have so many marriages in Sahaja Yoga
– I mean 1% marriages fail, 1%. They have

01:02:50.430 --> 01:02:55.350
beautiful children, they are living very well,
they have good houses. Those who were really

01:02:55.350 --> 01:03:02.350
hippies had nothing, are having nice houses
and everything they have. Also some of them,

01:03:03.310 --> 01:03:10.310
were “Oh, so I am now fortunately, I am
without job.” And I said, “What, you are

01:03:10.910 --> 01:03:17.180
very fortunate?” “Yea, now I am without
job. Very happy about it.” So I told the

01:03:17.180 --> 01:03:24.180
gentleman that if you are not going to stick
to one job, you are not going to come to Sahaja

01:03:24.840 --> 01:03:31.840
Yoga. And that fellow today has a big car,
a nice wife, children and a house.

01:03:34.770 --> 01:03:41.770
So all these ideas of stupid freedom must
be given up. One has to come to a balance

01:03:46.119 --> 01:03:53.119
and value your life. You must value it. Human
life is very valuable. With what great difficulty

01:03:54.960 --> 01:04:01.960
God has created you and what are we doing
with it? The whole society has to take a turn

01:04:13.780 --> 01:04:20.780
and think of living happily – if the husband
and wife, I mean such a relationship, husband

01:04:22.500 --> 01:04:29.500
and wife cannot live together, then how do
we expect this world to have United Nations?

01:04:30.240 --> 01:04:33.920
We cannot – it is falsehood.

01:04:33.920 --> 01:04:40.920
In Sahaja Yoga we don’t have divorces – we
have sometimes, sometimes we have, is allowed.

01:04:47.950 --> 01:04:53.070
But that is mostly when they are married beforehand
– fallen in love, now they are rising in

01:04:53.070 --> 01:04:56.869
love, falling in love again, again falling,
rising in love again… how many times they

01:04:56.869 --> 01:05:03.869
fall in love God only knows. It’s a funny
stuff going on. We have to face the reality.

01:05:09.349 --> 01:05:14.369
So just worrying about these things, what
we should do, is to first of all become wise

01:05:14.369 --> 01:05:21.369
and understand the problems. We can all solve
it. It is very simple, it is very simple to

01:05:21.950 --> 01:05:24.830
solve the problems.

01:05:24.830 --> 01:05:31.830
First of all we have to enter into the Kingdom
of God. And secondly, that it solves your

01:05:35.940 --> 01:05:42.599
problems. Just worrying about poor people,
it’s also a kind of a fashion these days.

01:05:42.599 --> 01:05:47.470
Because when I went to Switzerland, I met
a lady. She said, “I am very guilty.”

01:05:47.470 --> 01:05:48.460
I said, “Why?”

01:05:48.460 --> 01:05:49.210
“Because of Afghanistan.”

01:05:49.210 --> 01:05:50.359
I said, “Are you Afghani?”

01:05:50.359 --> 01:05:53.160
“No, but I am guilty about Afghanistan.”

01:05:53.160 --> 01:05:57.500
“What have you got to do with Afghanistan?”

01:05:57.500 --> 01:05:58.040
“Nothing.”

01:05:58.040 --> 01:06:05.040
So it’s kind of an idea - what are we doing
about it? But a Sahaja Yogi does, Sahaja Yogi

01:06:08.080 --> 01:06:15.080
finds out ways and methods of creating a convenient
life – a life where you can earn, you can

01:06:21.560 --> 01:06:28.560
live… we do it – we have done, I have
so many examples. Because it’s a collective

01:06:31.410 --> 01:06:38.240
life also you help each other. We didn’t
have rich people in Sahaja Yoga many because

01:06:38.240 --> 01:06:43.099
they seldom come to Sahaja Yoga. They go to
false gurus because they can purchase the

01:06:43.099 --> 01:06:50.099
guru – they can’t purchase Me. So mostly
the rich never come here. Bureaucrats also

01:06:50.200 --> 01:06:56.700
don’t come, politicians don’t come. So
those people who come to Me are the people

01:06:56.700 --> 01:07:03.700
who can easily solve the problem because they
are so collective, they can solve the problem.

01:07:07.810 --> 01:07:14.810
You’ll be surprised, I went to Turkey – My
husband was not so for it – everybody said,

01:07:16.930 --> 01:07:23.050
“That’s a Muslim country, this, that.”
I went to a Muslim country that was Turkey,

01:07:23.050 --> 01:07:30.050
and a woman, I just said I must go. But I
was surprised, they worshipped Mother, they

01:07:31.920 --> 01:07:37.930
worshipped their mothers. And they were so
beautiful – so many. In one shot, we got

01:07:37.930 --> 01:07:44.930
70 people – serious Sahaja Yogis. But do
you know when I reached there, people from

01:07:45.450 --> 01:07:52.450
America, from Australia, from all over the
world arrived there in Turkey to help Me.

01:07:52.670 --> 01:07:58.920
I mean I was so enamored to see My children
coming, arriving there on their own - those

01:07:58.920 --> 01:08:05.920
who could afford it. And the Turkish people
were so beautiful, I tell you. I found they

01:08:06.930 --> 01:08:09.000
are the same everywhere.

01:08:09.000 --> 01:08:16.000
There’s only a skin deep difference, I tell
you, otherwise we are just the same. So all

01:08:18.000 --> 01:08:25.000
these problems can be easily solved – there’s
nothing so serious about it. There is

01:09:00.650 --> 01:09:07.650
a very great thing no doubt, but unless and
until you are connected, it is like telephoning

01:09:16.270 --> 01:09:23.270
without connection. There are people in India
who’ll go on saying “Rama Rama Rama Rama

01:09:27.279 --> 01:09:33.210
Rama” like that. And the chakra of Rama
itself will be caught. They’ll be saying

01:09:33.210 --> 01:09:39.540
“Shiva Shiva Shiva Shiva” and the heart
chakra, where Shiva resides, it will be caught.

01:09:39.540 --> 01:09:46.540
The reason is, supposing you want to meet
the Queen – now if you go to Buckingham

01:09:49.960 --> 01:09:55.810
Palace and go on saying “Elizabeth, Elizabeth,
Elizabeth” – you’ll be arrested! And

01:09:55.810 --> 01:10:02.810
you’ll end up in a jail!

01:10:05.400 --> 01:10:12.400
So you must have some connection, there should
be some protocol. Now if it is for kings and

01:10:18.050 --> 01:10:25.050
prime ministers, what about God? He’s not
in your pocket. But once you are realized,

01:10:28.420 --> 01:10:34.020
even once you take the name, it is sufficient.
What is there? He’s at your disposal all

01:10:34.020 --> 01:10:41.020
the time there. But you have to have connection.
Now you are the citizens say of England, or

01:10:41.440 --> 01:10:46.570
some place, all right so your government is
looking after you. Whether you are satisfied

01:10:46.570 --> 01:10:51.980
or not is not the point. But they are looking
after you. But if you enter into the Kingdom

01:10:51.980 --> 01:10:58.980
of God, then see the efficiency of this Kingdom.
You’ll be amazed if I tell you how things

01:11:02.980 --> 01:11:09.980
work out. So amazing

01:11:41.920 --> 01:11:48.920
it is, so amazing. See first of all they say
Kundalini has to rise. Then it sometimes comes

01:11:55.690 --> 01:12:02.690
back to the centers which are needing more
help. So it is like a rope you can say, which

01:12:03.400 --> 01:12:10.400
has many strings in it, very thin ones just
like a hair, and one by one they open out.

01:12:13.780 --> 01:12:20.780
So first, very few of them pierce through,
open out the Sahasrara, by which you relax

01:12:22.500 --> 01:12:29.500
