like that. But once you are connected properly

01:12:31.040 --> 01:12:38.040
then there’s no problem. But it is instantaneous,
no doubt about it. But for that you have to

01:12:42.110 --> 01:12:49.110
come to our centers, don’t have to pay anything,
just spend some time and you have to master

01:12:50.070 --> 01:12:52.950
it, that’s all.

01:12:52.950 --> 01:12:59.950
There’s a question, what purpose do we have
on this planet?

01:13:01.469 --> 01:13:08.469
The purpose of our existence is to prove that
God’s creation is the most successful thing.

01:13:15.790 --> 01:13:20.320
That’s the purpose.

01:13:20.320 --> 01:13:27.320
About Me, I will not talk - I am sorry. You
better get your realization and try to find

01:13:44.680 --> 01:13:50.020
out about Me, because those who have talked
