01:14:15.639 --> 01:14:22.639
- try to know Me. Because I have to do some
jobs, all right and for that, I want to live.

01:14:27.739 --> 01:14:34.739
People are really sometimes so funny. Even
otherwise they behave in such a funny manner

01:14:35.130 --> 01:14:41.460
that I can’t understand. As if I am going
to take away their property or something.

01:14:41.460 --> 01:14:48.460
I am here to give you something that is very
important. Sort of you can say I am here to

01:14:49.750 --> 01:14:56.750
complete the work of Christ, Mohammed and
