01:15:08.940 --> 01:15:15.940
Yes please…. When you will give to others,
you will receive the blessings. That’s what

01:15:37.830 --> 01:15:44.830
it is absolutely 100%. He said so many things.
I mean just explaining Sahaja Yoga throughout

01:15:45.650 --> 01:15:51.070
I think.

