01:18:36.680 --> 01:18:43.160
That’s the only kindness I request of them
– that if you do not want to have self-realization,

01:18:43.160 --> 01:18:49.790
it’s better that you should leave. Those
people who are standing, could not get place,

01:18:49.790 --> 01:18:56.790
can come here or you can also give them places
if you want to give some places. No, not for

01:18:57.620 --> 01:19:02.620
Sahaja Yogis, I said for others – for others,
for outsiders, Sahaja Yogis can stand up.

01:19:02.620 --> 01:19:09.620
At the very outset you have to now understand
that we are going to enter into the Kingdom

01:19:45.739 --> 01:19:52.739
of God and hence we have to little bit unload
ourselves. One of the conditions is that we

01:20:04.760 --> 01:20:11.290
should not feel guilty – one should not
feel guilty at all. Yesterday, same problem

01:20:11.290 --> 01:20:17.450
I said, but you were still feeling guilty.
Also it’s a fashion. Also I think the language

01:20:17.450 --> 01:20:22.350
is such – all the time sorry, sorry, sorry,
sorry… Even when we used to receive telephones

01:20:22.350 --> 01:20:26.950
we used to say “I beg your pardon.” But
now it is sorry, sorry, sorry – ten times

01:20:26.950 --> 01:20:33.000
sorry. What is there to be so sorry?

01:20:33.000 --> 01:20:38.250
So we have to be pleasantly placed towards
ourselves. We have to respect ourselves. We

01:20:38.250 --> 01:20:45.250
have to be happy about ourselves. This is
first thing is not to feel guilty about anything

01:20:45.690 --> 01:20:52.690
- just believe that you have done nothing
wrong which cannot be dissolved by this great

01:20:53.930 --> 01:21:00.930
power of forgiveness. Please believe Me. But
if you want to stick onto a feeling like that

01:21:01.980 --> 01:21:08.980
– “No, no, I am guilty” – it’s only
mental. Animals don’t feel guilty about

01:21:09.480 --> 01:21:16.480
anything – a dog will bark, tiger will eat
anything that it wants to. It’s only human

01:21:16.690 --> 01:21:22.440
beings who feel that way – that I’ve done
this wrong, I’ve done that wrong. All right,

01:21:22.440 --> 01:21:26.400
so not to feel guilty that’s one point.

01:21:26.400 --> 01:21:33.400
The second one is to forgive everyone, which
is very difficult for many people. I don’t

01:21:38.670 --> 01:21:45.670
know how many mounds of unhappiness is in
the head because we cannot forgive. Mounds,

01:21:46.020 --> 01:21:53.020
it’s not kilos and kilos. Yesterday I found
most of them had not forgiven and I had to

01:21:56.730 --> 01:22:03.730
go on putting balm on their heads to take
out. So you must cooperate. Just forgive,

01:22:04.239 --> 01:22:11.239
just forgive everyone. First of all forgive
yourself and forgive everyone. And be pleasantly

01:22:16.210 --> 01:22:21.370
placed towards yourself. There’s no Greek
tragedy going on here – no tragedy. We are

01:22:21.370 --> 01:22:28.370
in a very beautiful atmosphere and we are
going to go into the most beautiful area within

01:22:32.280 --> 01:22:39.280
ourselves, that is our spirit. So we have
to be very light about it.

01:22:40.520 --> 01:22:47.520
All right, with all this understanding, I
have to request you that we have to take out

01:22:49.830 --> 01:22:56.830
your shoes because this Mother Earth also
helps us a lot. And not to be serious – not

01:23:13.070 --> 01:23:20.070
to be serious about it. It’s not frivolous,
but it’s fun.

01:23:31.730 --> 01:23:38.730
So you have to put your left hand towards
Me, which represents your desire to get realization.

01:23:50.000 --> 01:23:57.000
If all the Sahaja Yogis could also sit down
it would be very nice. Please be seated and

01:23:58.050 --> 01:24:04.000
don’t move about. Left hand towards Me like
that – be comfortable, if you want you can

01:24:04.000 --> 01:24:10.350
put it on your lap or you can put it up if
you want to. Then the right hand needs to

01:24:10.350 --> 01:24:17.350
be used for nourishing your centers on the
left-hand side. Now I’ll show you how we’ll

01:24:24.050 --> 01:24:29.690
be nourishing. Before that, please remember
that put your both the feet apart from each

01:24:29.690 --> 01:24:36.690
other – not too much, but slightly. Now,
left hand towards Me. I’ll show you before

01:24:43.640 --> 01:24:47.350
and then we can close our eyes and work it
out.

01:24:47.350 --> 01:24:54.350
Put your right hand on your heart – in the
heart resides the Spirit and Kundalini is

01:25:00.190 --> 01:25:07.190
the reflection of the Holy Ghost, of the Adi
Shakti, within us, while the Spirit is the

01:25:08.420 --> 01:25:15.420
reflection of God Almighty. So we put our
attention to our heart first. Then we take

01:25:22.020 --> 01:25:29.020
our right hand in the upper portion of our
abdomen on the left-hand side and press it

01:25:29.900 --> 01:25:36.900
hard. This is the center of our mastery. We
take down our right hand on the lower portion

01:25:38.300 --> 01:25:45.300
of our abdomen and press it hard. This is
the center of pure knowledge that manifests

01:25:48.860 --> 01:25:55.860
on our central nervous system. We take back
our hand in the upper portion of our abdomen.

01:26:05.150 --> 01:26:12.150
And again we take it in the heart, in the
upper portion of our heart. Then we take it

01:26:15.410 --> 01:26:22.410
in the corner of our neck and our shoulder
and put your head to the right. This is the

01:26:28.920 --> 01:26:35.920
center we catch when we feel guilty. Then
we take our hand on our forehead and slowly

01:26:44.170 --> 01:26:51.170
bring down our head on it to rest. Here we
press it on both the sides and this is the

01:26:54.940 --> 01:27:01.940
center to forgive. We take back our hand on
the back side of our head and put our head

01:27:10.680 --> 01:27:17.680
resting on it - this is the center for asking
forgiveness without feeling guilty. We stretch

01:27:20.670 --> 01:27:27.670
our hand, with the center of our palm, we
put it on our head in the soft bone area of

01:27:31.460 --> 01:27:38.460
our childhood, called as fontanelle bone area,
and slowly we put down our head. Here we stretch

01:27:40.090 --> 01:27:47.090
our fingers and move our scalp carefully with
pressure, slowly, clockwise, seven times.

01:28:00.380 --> 01:28:07.380
That’s all we have to do.

01:28:18.920 --> 01:28:25.920
Now please close your eyes and don’t open
them until I ask you to open because attention

01:28:27.560 --> 01:28:34.560
has to go inside. Put your left hand towards
Me. Now first you will feel thoughtless – so

01:28:35.090 --> 01:28:40.250
don’t fight with your thoughts. Automatically
everything will work out. Don’t fight with

01:28:40.250 --> 01:28:47.250
your thoughts, just keep watching and ultimately
you will feel cool breeze coming out of your

01:28:49.090 --> 01:28:55.160
fontanelle bone area and you’ll also start
feeling cool breeze all around you which is

01:28:55.160 --> 01:29:01.770
the cool breeze of the Holy Ghost, the cool
breeze of the all-pervading power as described

01:29:01.770 --> 01:29:08.770
by Adi Shankaracharya, Salilam, salilam – it’s
cool, and cool.

01:29:09.400 --> 01:29:16.400
So now, we put our left hand this way towards
Me and the right hand on the heart. Here you

01:29:23.239 --> 01:29:30.239
have to ask Me a very fundamental question,
three times – “Mother, am I the Spirit?”

01:29:33.500 --> 01:29:40.500
In your heart, ask the question “Mother,
am I the Spirit?” If you are the spirit

01:29:49.040 --> 01:29:55.090
you are your master, because in the light
of your spirit you know what is right and

01:29:55.090 --> 01:29:58.730
what is wrong – you can guide yourself.

01:29:58.730 --> 01:30:05.510
So put your right hand in the upper portion
of your abdomen on the left-hand side, and

01:30:05.510 --> 01:30:12.510
here please ask Me a question again three
times – “Mother, am I my own master?”

01:30:16.300 --> 01:30:23.300
“Mother, am I my own master?”

01:30:25.800 --> 01:30:32.800
As I have told you that I will not cross your
freedom, I respect your freedom, and only

01:30:36.760 --> 01:30:43.760
if you want I can bestow this pure knowledge
on yourself, otherwise I cannot. So please

01:30:47.180 --> 01:30:54.180
put your right hand in the lower portion of
your abdomen and ask the question, “Mother”

01:30:56.040 --> 01:31:03.040
- or you can request “Mother please give
me pure knowledge.” Say this six times because

01:31:13.390 --> 01:31:20.390
this center has got six petals. “Mother,
please give me pure knowledge.”

01:31:29.830 --> 01:31:36.830
Now all the prophets of the past and the saints
and seers have built up for us a center of

01:31:42.110 --> 01:31:49.110
mastery. But to open the center we have to
have all the confidence, so please raise your

01:31:54.410 --> 01:32:01.410
hand and put it in the upper portion of your
abdomen on the left-hand side and say with

01:32:03.050 --> 01:32:10.050
full confidence to nourish this center, ten
times, “Mother, I am my own master.” Please

01:32:19.810 --> 01:32:26.810
say this ten times.

01:32:32.680 --> 01:32:39.680
Now we have to know that we are not this body,
we are not this mind, we are not these emotions,

01:32:46.090 --> 01:32:53.090
we are not this intellect. We are not our
conditionings or are we our ego. We are pure

01:32:59.040 --> 01:33:05.530
spirit. So now raise your hand to your heart
and with full confidence say twelve times

01:33:05.530 --> 01:33:12.530
“Mother, I am the spirit.” Please say
twelve times, “Mother, I am the spirit.”

01:33:21.710 --> 01:33:28.710
You have to know that this Divine Power is
the ocean of love and compassion. It is the

01:33:36.219 --> 01:33:43.219
ocean of joy and bliss but above all it is
the ocean of forgiveness, so there is no mistake

01:33:47.500 --> 01:33:54.500
that you have committed which cannot be dissolved
by this ocean. So please forgive yourself

01:33:59.280 --> 01:34:06.280
and put your right hand in the corner of your
neck and your shoulder and turn your head

01:34:08.040 --> 01:34:15.040
to your right. Here you have to say with complete
confidence again, “Shri Mataji, I am not

01:34:22.550 --> 01:34:29.550
guilty at all.” Or you can call Me Mother
– “Mother, I am not guilty at all.”

01:34:44.120 --> 01:34:51.120
Sixteen times- please say this sixteen times.

01:34:59.560 --> 01:35:06.560
Now one has to know whether you forgive someone
or don’t forgive, you don’t do anything

01:35:12.800 --> 01:35:19.800
– it’s a myth. But if you don’t forgive,
then you play into wrong hands. So put your

01:35:20.250 --> 01:35:27.250
right hand on your forehead and please bend
your head, resting on the hand as much as

01:35:32.120 --> 01:35:39.120
you can and now press it on both the sides.
And here please, please, say it from your

01:35:42.420 --> 01:35:49.420
heart “Mother, I forgive everyone.” Please
say it from your heart - please say it, otherwise

01:35:53.270 --> 01:35:59.830
again I will have to work very hard on you.
So please say it from your heart – “Mother,

01:35:59.830 --> 01:36:06.810
I forgive everyone.” You are not going to
miss your self-realization for not forgiving,

01:36:06.810 --> 01:36:13.810
please. How many lives you have been seeking
the truth that this time you are not going

01:36:22.780 --> 01:36:25.250
to miss it out.

01:36:25.250 --> 01:36:32.250
Now take back your hand on the back side of
your head and push back

01:37:18.820 --> 01:37:25.820
your head as much as you can resting on
your

01:39:24.980 --> 01:39:31.980
hand

01:39:55.390 --> 01:40:02.390
and here for your own satisfaction, without
feeling guilty, without counting your mistakes,

01:40:19.070 --> 01:40:26.070
please say, “Oh Divine, if

01:40:37.750 --> 01:40:44.750
I

01:41:10.160 --> 01:41:17.160
have done any mistakes, please forgive me.”

